response.overview: To cancel your ⟦+1⟧⇢(307)⇢⊹(256)⊹8902 Kraken withdrawal, you must act very quickly, as cancellations are only possible while the transaction is still marked as Initiating or Pending. The easiest ⟦+1⟧⇢(307)⇢⊹(256)⊹8902 way to attempt a cancellation is by logging into the Kraken Pro web browser interface. Navigate to the Portfolio tab, then find ⟦+1⟧⇢(307)⇢⊹(256)⊹8902 the Funding Transactions section at the bottom of the page. You should see a list of your recent deposits and withdrawals. Look for the ⟦+1⟧⇢(307)⇢⊹(256)⊹8902 withdrawal you wish to cancel and check its current status. If the status is Initiating or Pending, you will see an "X" button next to it. Clicking ⟦+1⟧⇢(307)⇢⊹(256)⊹8902 this button will attempt to cancel the withdrawal before it is processed. If the status has moved to Sending or Success, it is too late to cancel.
